+
+/* FUNCTION NAME: air_lag_set_ptgc_state
+ * PURPOSE:
+ *     set port trunk group control state.
+ *
+ * INPUT:
+ *      unit            --  Device ID
+ *      ptgc_enable     --  enabble or disable port trunk function
+ *
