+ * PURPOSE:
+ *      Get port matrix from the specified device.
+ *
+ * INPUT:
+ *      unit            --  Unit id
+ *      port            --  Port id
+ *
+ * OUTPUT:
+ *      p_port_bitmap   --  Matrix port bitmap
