+/* FUNCTION NAME:   air_vlan_reset
+ * PURPOSE:
+ *      Destroy the vlan in the specified device.
+ * INPUT:
+ *      unit        -- unit id
+ *      vid         -- vlan id
+ * OUTPUT:
